T02TD1193E:25a-26: nges par brjod pa bla ma zhes bya ba'i rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las kyang //
T02TD1193E:25a-27: ri sul dang ni ri rtse dang /
T02TD1193E:25a-28: chu bo chen po'i ngogs dag dang //
T02TD1193E:25a-29: rgya mtsho chen po'i 'gram dag dang /
T02TD1193E:25a-30: shing gcig dang ni dge ba'i gnas //
T02TD1193E:25a-31: ma mo'i khyim mam dur khrod dam //
T02TD1193E:25a-32: sna tshogs dben pa'i sa phyogs sam //
T02TD1193E:25a-33: lha khang dang ni mchod rten dang /
T02TD1193E:25a-34: khyim mam bzhi mdo dag tu ni //
T02TD1193E:25a-35: sgrub pa po yis sbyor bsgrubs na //
T02TD1193E:25a-38: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa zhes bya ba'i rtsa ba'i rgyud chen po las kyang /
T02TD1193E:25a-39: dgon pa chen po'i ngos phyogs sam //
T02TD1193E:25a-40: rab tu rnam par dben pa dang /
T02TD1193E:25a-41: ri bo dben pa'i sa phyogs su //
T02TD1193E:25a-42: ting 'dzin byas na dngos grub thob //
T02TD1193E:25a-44: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud kyi sgor zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis dkyil 'khor la sogs pa'i las byed pa dang /
T02TD1193E:25a-45: sgrub pa la 'jug pa rnams ni /
T02TD1193E:25b-0: dgon pa dang nags @25b 'dab la sogs par sgrub kyi /
T02TD1193E:25b-1: gzhan du grong dang 'du 'dzi la sogs par dkyil 'khor la sogs pa'i las byas na /
T02TD1193E:25b-2: dam tshig nyams shing ngan 'gro rnams su skye ste /
T02TD1193E:25b-3: dngos grub chen po la rgyab kyis phyogs shing /
T02TD1193E:25b-4: rnam par grol ba thob par mi 'gyur ro //
T02TD1193E:25b-5: de bas na 'di nyid las kyang nags 'dab la sogs pa dben pa dang /
T02TD1193E:25b-6: khyim gyi dbus su dkyil 'khor bya //
T02TD1193E:25b-7: zhes 'byung bas na dgon pa'i khyim du bya'o //
T02TD1193E:25b-8: de la spyir rnal 'byor chen po'i sgrub pa po rnams kyi gnas khang ni dgon pa dang /
T02TD1193E:25b-9: bas mtha' la sogs par rnal 'byor pa'i gnas khang brtsigs te /
T02TD1193E:25b-10: de yang khang pa sum brtsegs su byas la /
T02TD1193E:25b-11: 'og khang du ni mchod pa la sogs pa longs spyod kyi gnas bya'o //
T02TD1193E:25b-12: bar khang du ni rnga dang gling bu dang dung dang cha lang la sogs pa rol mo'i cha rkyen dag gzhag go / de'i steng du ni rnal 'byor pho mo dang /
T02TD1193E:25b-14: sku dang 'dris la sogs pa bkod de /
T02TD1193E:25b-15: de'i dbus su dkyil 'khor dang mchod pa la sogs pa zhes 'byung ngo //
T02TD1193E:25b-17: khyim gyi dbus su dkyil 'khor ni //
T02TD1193E:25b-18: dkyil 'khor dam pa bri bar bya //
T02TD1193E:25b-20: de'i dbus te gong ma'i nang du bya zhes bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:25b-21: lhag ma ni brda phrad sla'o //
T02TD1193E:25b-22: phyag rgya de yis bsnyen pa yis //
T02TD1193E:25b-23: de dus shukra ldan byung ba //
T02TD1193E:25b-24: zhes bya ba ni lha mo de nyid tshul bzhin du byin gyis brlabs la /
T02TD1193E:25b-25: snyoms par zhugs te shukra dbab pa de mkha' de nyid du ro 'dzin gyis slob mas blang ba'am /
T02TD1193E:25b-26: shin tu ma goms pa zhig na khar blugs par bya'o //
T02TD1193E:25b-27: dang po sprin gyi tshul can gyi //
T02TD1193E:25b-28: grub nas sgyu ma lta bur bya //
T02TD1193E:25b-30: rnal 'byor pas thog mar gnas gong ma lta bur tshul bzhin du dbang thob pas /
T02TD1193E:25b-31: yun ring du bsgrubs te thog mar grub pa'i mtshan ma /
T02TD1193E:25b-32: sprin lta bu'i sna tshogs pa'i 'od dang snang ba dag 'byung ngo //
T02TD1193E:25b-33: de goms pa las sgyu ma lta bur 'gyur ro ;
T02TD1193E:25b-34: / der yang mthar thug rmi lam lta bu ste //
T02TD1193E:25b-35: gnyid log ma log mthong bzhin du //
T02TD1193E:25b-36: zhes pa la mthar thug pa'i dga' ba la yun ring du bzhag ste /
T02TD1193E:25b-37: dper na gnyid log pa'i rmi lam na gter rnyed pa rmis pa'i gzugs brnyan /
T02TD1193E:26a-0: sad na dngos po med kyang gzugs brnyan yid la yod @26a * //
T02TD1193E:26a-1: pa ltar gnyid log pa dang /
T02TD1193E:26a-2: ma log pa dang 'gro ba dang 'dug pa thams cad du /
T02TD1193E:26a-3: mthar thug pa'i bde ba la mnyam par gzhag pa'i don /
T02TD1193E:26a-4: mtshan ma mthong nas sgrub pa ste /
T02TD1193E:26a-5: rnal 'byor phyag rgya grub par gyur /
T02TD1193E:26a-7: de ltar yun ring du bsgoms pas rnam par rtog pa thams cad dang bral to /
T02TD1193E:26a-8: rim gyis 'od gsal pa thob pa'i mtshan ma rgyud las byung ba rnams byung ba ni rnal 'byor phyag rgya ste /
T02TD1193E:26a-9: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub ces bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:26a-10: lhag ma ni brda phrad sla'o //
T02TD1193E:26a-11: shes rab thabs kyi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1193E:26a-12: de las sa ni skye bar byed //
T02TD1193E:26a-13: ces pa la snyoms par 'jug pa'i tshe dbang po sprad pa las cung zhig sra ba ni sa'i mtshan ma ste /
T02TD1193E:26a-14: de las ni skyed par byed ces bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26a-15: byang chub sems kyi rgyun babs las //
T02TD1193E:26a-16: chu ru yang ni gyur pa yin //
T02TD1193E:26a-17: zhes pa la sha shi zhu ba'i rgyun brlan pas na chu zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26a-18: reg pa las ni me 'byung ste //
T02TD1193E:26a-20: gnas skabs de na me'i tsha ba bskyed pa la bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26a-22: bde ba'i ro gang gis brjod du med pas nam mkha' 'o //
T02TD1193E:26a-23: de ltar byung ba las gyur pa'i bde ba ni bde ba chen po ma yin te /
T02TD1193E:26a-24: ye shes grub pa zhes bya ba rnal 'byor chen po'i sgrub thabs las kyang /
T02TD1193E:26a-25: dbang po gnyis byung bde ba ni //
T02TD1193E:26a-26: de nyid yin zhes skye ngan smra'i //
T02TD1193E:26a-27: de ni bde ba che zhes te //
T02TD1193E:26a-28: rgyal ba rnams kyis ma gsungs so //
T02TD1193E:26a-29: bde gshegs kun gyi ye shes ni //
T02TD1193E:26a-30: rang nyid ngo bo nyid mkhyen la //
T02TD1193E:26a-31: bde ba kun gyi gtsor gyur la //
T02TD1193E:26a-32: bde ba chen po zhes bshad do //
T02TD1193E:26a-33: bde ba de yang mi spang ste //
T02TD1193E:26a-34: chags dang mnyam pa'i bde med de //
T02TD1193E:26a-35: de ni rgyal ba rnams la dbul //
T02TD1193E:26a-36: 'dod pa'i don kun longs spyod cing //
T02TD1193E:26a-37: smad pa dag tu mi bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26a-39: de ltar 'byung ba'i bde ba ni //
T02TD1193E:26a-40: bde ba yin gyi chen po ni ma yin zhes pa'i don /
T02TD1193E:26a-42: mthar thug gis ni gang bskyed pa ;
T02TD1193E:26a-43: / de ni mthar thug yin zhes brjod pa ni /
T02TD1193E:26a-44: rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba gnyis su med pa'i skad cig ma la bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26a-45: thams cad bde ba gcig pu pa //
T02TD1193E:26a-46: rang bzhin mthar thug yin par brjod //
T02TD1193E:26a-48: thams cad bde ba ni rtog pa thams cad dang bral bas /
T02TD1193E:26b-0: thams cad dang @26b bral gcig pu zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26b-1: de sus rtog pa ni bde ba gcig pu yang yin la /
T02TD1193E:26b-2: mthar thug pa yang yin pa'i don de'i dngos po gang zhe na /
T02TD1193E:26b-3: phyag rgya'i rgyu dang rnam bral zhing //
T02TD1193E:26b-5: mthar thug pa'i skabs su sngags dang phyag rgya la sogs pa rnams la mi rtog pas bral zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26b-6: snying rje thabs ldan rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1193E:26b-7: zhes pa la stong pa nyid dang /
T02TD1193E:26b-9: rtag tu mi 'bral zhing gnas zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26b-10: byang chub sems zhes bya ba ni //
T02TD1193E:26b-11: kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i sems te /
T02TD1193E:26b-12: sems can thams cad byang chub la dgod pa'i bsam pas snyoms par zhugs pa'i sa bon las /
T02TD1193E:26b-13: sku dang dkyil 'khor la sogs 'byung ste /
T02TD1193E:26b-14: 'gro ba'i don spyad pa na kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems so //
T02TD1193E:26b-15: de'i bde ba spros pa thams cad dang bral ba ni /
T02TD1193E:26b-16: don dam pa'i bde ba chen po ste /
T02TD1193E:26b-17: de ni don dam pa byang chub kyi sems zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26b-18: rnam gcig tu na he ru ka'i sku chu zla lta bu thams cad kyi bdag nyid du snang bas /
T02TD1193E:26b-19: thabs sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba 'dren par mdzad pa ni /
T02TD1193E:26b-20: snying rje ste kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems yin la /
T02TD1193E:26b-21: don dam par sgyu ma'i mkhan po ltar rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba la bya'o //
T02TD1193E:26b-22: yang na mthar thug pa'i bde ba chen po de ni shes rab dang snying rje zung du 'brel pa'i bdag nyid yin pas /
T02TD1193E:26b-23: byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
T02TD1193E:26b-24: 'phags pa dri ma med par grags pas bstan pa'i mdo las kyang /
T02TD1193E:26b-25: shes rab dang ni snying rje gnyis ldan la //
T02TD1193E:26b-26: byang chub sems zhes bya ba shes pa dang //
T02TD1193E:26b-27: slob dpon klu sgrub kyi zhal snga nas kyis rim pa lnga'i sgrub pa mdzad pa las kyang /
T02TD1193E:26b-28: shes rab snying rje gcig pa ni //
T02TD1193E:26b-29: shes nas blo ni nges byas te //
T02TD1193E:26b-30: rim 'di sangs rgyas spyod yul te //
T02TD1193E:26b-33: de bas na mthar thug pa'i bde ba chen po de ni /
T02TD1193E:26b-34: shes rab dang snying rje'i bdag nyid yin pas na /
T02TD1193E:26b-35: byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
T02TD1193E:26b-36: de la sgrub pa pos dang por thog ma med pa nas kyi sdug bsngal dran par byas la /
T02TD1193E:27a-0: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde ba 'dod pas 'du 'dzi thams cad yongs su spang bar bya zhing tha na rgyal srid kyi dbang phyug la yang sdug bsngal du bsam @27a * //
T02TD1193E:27a-2: gnyis par ni til 'bru tsam la yang dngos por 'dzin pa'i blo spang bar bya'o //
T02TD1193E:27a-3: gsum par ni don dam pa'i bden pa la dad pas lus dang srog la yang ltos pa med par bya ste /
T02TD1193E:27a-4: 'du shes gsum pa'i tshul du dmigs te /
T02TD1193E:27a-5: de bas na bhu zhes bya ba ni zas la spyod pa ste /
T02TD1193E:27a-6: de tsam zhig rjes su dran pa dang 'du 'dzi thams cad spong bar byed cing /
T02TD1193E:27a-7: dka' thub dang brtul zhugs so zhes gang la yang sems par mi byed cing rang gi sgrub pa'i don la rtse gcig tu dmigs pa'o //
T02TD1193E:27a-8: su zhes bya ba ni gnyid log pa ste rnam par shes pa 'di dag la ma rig pas nye bar mtshon pas mngon sum du byed do //
T02TD1193E:27a-9: ma rig pa lcags kyu 'dra ba des rnam par shes pa gang la yang 'dren par mi byed de /
T02TD1193E:27a-10: 'od gsal ba nyid mngon sum du byed cing dri ma med pa'i ngo bo nyid rtse gcig tu sems pa'o //
T02TD1193E:27a-11: ku zhes bya ba ni bshang sar 'gro ba ste bshad gcu'i dor ba'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:27a-12: de tsam zhig dran par byed cing 'du 'dzi spong bar byed la /
T02TD1193E:27a-13: lus dang tshor ba dang dbang po la sogs pa'i ngo bo nyid la sems par mi byed cing /
T02TD1193E:27a-14: gang sgrub pa'i don la skad cig kyang mi g-yel bar sgrub ces bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:27a-15: sems de la skad cig dang zhag dang zla ba dang /
T02TD1193E:27a-16: lo la sogs par gnas par byas la /
T02TD1193E:27a-17: lhun gyis grub ste de'i skabs su ni gsang sngags dang dka' thub dang /
T02TD1193E:27a-18: sbyin sreg la sogs pa mi dgos pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:27a-19: mdor bsdus sems bsdus tshul can te //
T02TD1193E:27a-20: zhes pa la dper na 'chi ba'i sems gcig tu gyur cing rtog pa chung ba ltar /
T02TD1193E:27a-21: mthar thug pa'i sems de yang rtog pa dang bral ba /
T02TD1193E:27a-22: nam mkha'i ngang tshul can de la ni sems bsdus zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:27a-23: de lta bu'i ngang der spyod lam thams cad du rig pa lnga phyi de la 'bab pas na /
T02TD1193E:27a-25: rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba 'od gsal ba ni /
T02TD1193E:27a-26: dkyil 'khor snying po yin la de la gnyis su med pa'i ye shes dang /
T02TD1193E:27a-27: mnyam du 'jug cing dbyer med par gyur pa ni /
T02TD1193E:27a-28: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa yang de zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:27a-31: // / da ni le'u bcu gcig pa bshad par bya ste /
T02TD1193E:27a-32: mnyam pa'i drag shul 'phral bar gtod //
T02TD1193E:27b-0: mig @27b dang dbugs la sogs pa ni sgrub pa ste /
T02TD1193E:27b-1: he ru ka'i mig gnyis drang por blta ba ni mnyam pa'o //
T02TD1193E:27b-2: 'phral bar gtod pa ni gyen du 'phral ba'i phyogs su blta ba'o //
T02TD1193E:27b-3: dus kun ltung byed yin par bshad //
T02TD1193E:27b-5: de ltar bltas pas bsgrub par bya ba sa la ltung ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:27b-6: mig 'bras gnyis po g-yon du gtod //
T02TD1193E:27b-7: g-yon du ba lta ba dbang blta ba'o //
T02TD1193E:27b-9: g-yon phyogs su mig gnyis bltas pas dbang du 'gyur ba'i don /
T02TD1193E:27b-10: g-yas su bltas pas kyang bsgrub par bya ba dbang du 'gyur ba'i don /
T02TD1193E:27b-11: yang mig gnyis sna bug gnyis kyi rtser bltas pas ni /
T02TD1193E:27b-12: rnam par gnon pa'i las 'grub po //
T02TD1193E:27b-13: de ni lta sangs bzhi bsgrub pa'o //
T02TD1193E:27b-15: dbugs phar gtong bas ni ltung bar byed pa yin la /
T02TD1193E:27b-16: gnas pas ni dbang du byed pa yin no //
T02TD1193E:27b-17: tshur brngubs pas ni 'gugs par byed pa yin no //
T02TD1193E:27b-18: de dag gi don gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:27b-19: ltung byed ljon shing bcud rnams su //
T02TD1193E:27b-21: sgrub pa'i shing gi bcud rnams 'gugs par byed do //
T02TD1193E:27b-22: dbugs gnas pa ni sgrub pa'i me tog rnams dbang du byed do //
T02TD1193E:27b-23: dbugs brngubs pas ni rdo rje'i shing shri ki sta bcud rnams sdud pa ste /
T02TD1193E:27b-24: de mthu dang ldan pas bsgrubs na //
T02TD1193E:27b-25: zla drug gis 'grub ces pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:27b-26: 'di la yid gnyis mi bya ste //
T02TD1193E:27b-27: sangs rgyas sgyu 'phrul mi bsam mo //
T02TD1193E:27b-29: 'di rnams sangs rgyas kyi sgyu 'phrul yin gyi /
T02TD1193E:27b-30: bdag gis thob bam mi thob ces bsam par mi bya ba'i don mthong ba bzhi po zhes pa ni /
T02TD1193E:27b-31: gong ma bzhi po la bya'o //
T02TD1193E:27b-32: lhag ma ni go sla bas ma bris so //
T02TD1193E:27b-33: na sogs ga sogs pa ni zhes pa ni bza' ba dam tshig ste /
T02TD1193E:27b-34: thog ma'i sha zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD1193E:27b-37: ga ni ba lang gi sha'o //
T02TD1193E:27b-38: ha ni glang po che'i sha'o //
T02TD1193E:27b-39: mthar thug sha ni rta'i sha ste /
T02TD1193E:27b-40: de rnams zos na 'grub par 'gyur ro zhes bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:27b-41: rigs bdun ni skye ba bdun pa'i grib ma bdun yod pa shi ba'i sha zos na 'grub po //
T02TD1193E:27b-42: yang na 'di pa shu 'am phyugs chen po zer te /
T02TD1193E:27b-43: de'i sha la sogs pas las 'grub ste /
T02TD1193E:27b-44: de'i mtshan ma ni grib ma bdun 'char ba dang /
T02TD1193E:28a-0: lus ga bur gyi dri dang @28a * //
T02TD1193E:28a-2: bshad gci gla rtsi bro ba dang //
T02TD1193E:28a-3: dkon mchog la dad pa dang /
T02TD1193E:28a-4: pha rol tu phyin pa kun dang ldan pa la sogs pa'o //
T02TD1193E:28a-5: kha cig de gsad pa de yin zer na ma yin te /
T02TD1193E:28a-6: nges par brjod pa bla ma'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:28a-8: gsad pa'i sbyor ba ma yin pas //
T02TD1193E:28a-9: 'chi ba med la mi bsregs shing //
T02TD1193E:28a-10: srog chags sna tshogs gdug pa dang //
T02TD1193E:28a-11: gang yang rung ba zar mi gzhug / de ni mtshan mo ma mthong bar //
T02TD1193E:28a-12: mi snang ba yi dbang phyug mchog /'di 'dra sngags pas rtogs nas ni //
T02TD1193E:28a-13: bdag gis bslangs te sbyin pa spyad //
T02TD1193E:28a-15: de'i sha dang rus pa la sogs pas grub pa sna tshogs 'byung ngo //
T02TD1193E:28a-16: khyad par du snying ga lte ba spyi bo na yod do //
T02TD1193E:28a-17: gong ma'i sha de rnams kyang rang bzhin gyis shi ba'am /
T02TD1193E:28a-18: rigs ngan dang shan pa la sogs pa las yon bdag gis nyos te zos pa ni dam pa rnams dgyes pa yin la /
T02TD1193E:28a-19: gzhan du sems can la gnod pas gsad dam /
T02TD1193E:28a-20: gsod du bcug pa'i sbyor ba la sogs pa rnams kyis blangs te zos na /
T02TD1193E:28a-22: dgongs pa lung bstan pa'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:28a-23: rnal 'byor pa ni bdag ces sma //
T02TD1193E:28a-25: srog chags gzhan rnams gsod par byed //
T02TD1193E:28a-26: dam tshig rnams ni de mi shes //
T02TD1193E:28a-31: srog gcod pa yi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1193E:28a-32: dam tshig nyams pa'i mchog tu 'gyur //
T02TD1193E:28a-33: sems can gnod pa byas tsam gyis //
T02TD1193E:28a-34: phyag rgya'i dngos grub thob mi 'gyur //
T02TD1193E:28a-35: de bas rnam pa thams cad du //
T02TD1193E:28a-36: sems can gnod pa spang bar bya'o //
T02TD1193E:28a-38: gong ma'i rdzas rnams blang zhes bya ba'i don /
T02TD1193E:28a-39: ku ru ku lle'i sgrub pa bshad //
T02TD1193E:28a-40: ces ba la sogs pa ni brda phrad sla bas ma bris so //
T02TD1193E:28a-41: le'u bcu gcig pa'i bshad pa'o /
T02TD1193E:28a-43: // /'di man chad brtag pa gnyis rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma 'chad de /
T02TD1193E:28a-44: de las kyang le'u dang po bshad pa ston to //
T02TD1193E:28a-45: 'dir sku gzugs rab tu gnas pa'i cho ga bstan pas na /
T02TD1193E:28b-0: sgo bsal bas ci rigs par shes par gyis shig / da ni @28b le'u gnyis pa'i bshad pa bstan te /
T02TD1193E:28b-1: 'di las shes rab dang ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba'i cho ga ston te //
T02TD1193E:28b-2: bcom ldan chos rnams thams cad kyi //
T02TD1193E:28b-3: ji ltar rgya mtshor ku ba bzhin //
T02TD1193E:28b-5: 'khor ba'i dngos po rgya mtsho las //
T02TD1193E:28b-6: chos kyi de bzhin nyid kyi pha rol tu 'gro bar 'dod pas zhes bya bar sbyar ro //
T02TD1193E:28b-7: de yang dper na rgya mtsho ni rgya che zhing zab kyang /
T02TD1193E:28b-8: thabs mkhas pa'i skyes bus ku ba gnyis gshibs pa la zhon te song na /
T02TD1193E:28b-9: mthar gyis pha rol gyi ngogs su phyin pa ltar /
T02TD1193E:28b-10: chos kyi dbyings las byung ba'i dngos grub rgya chen po ste /
T02TD1193E:28b-11: ji ltar thob par 'gyur zhes zhus pa'o //
T02TD1193E:28b-13: bdag med pa yis rnal 'byor bdag / yang na dpal ldan khrag 'thung sbyor //
T02TD1193E:28b-15: bdag med pa la 'jug pa dang /
T02TD1193E:28b-16: dpal he ru ka'i sku sgyu ma lta bu la skad cig tsam yang mi g-yeng ba'i sems kyis gnas shig bsgoms na /
T02TD1193E:28b-17: dngos grub thob po zhes pa'i don /
T02TD1193E:28b-18: de bas na rtsa ba las /
T02TD1193E:28b-19: skad cig tsam ni gzhan pa'i sems //
T02TD1193E:28b-22: lhag ma ni go sla bas ma dris so //
T02TD1193E:28b-23: rig pa lan cig byas pa yis //
T02TD1193E:28b-24: rtags ni de ma thag tu 'byung //
T02TD1193E:28b-26: shes rab dang mnyam par bzhag pas mthar thug pa'i dga' ba las ye shes 'byung ste /
T02TD1193E:28b-27: dngos grub 'byung zhes bya ba'i don //
T02TD1193E:28b-28: zla ba gcig tu gsang ba spyod //
T02TD1193E:28b-29: gang yang rung ba'i zla ba la sgrub ces byas te /
T02TD1193E:28b-30: rtags byung nas dngos grub blangs pa'i thabs so //
T02TD1193E:28b-31: gang du phyag rgya mi rnyed na //
T02TD1193E:28b-32: drin gyis phog pa'i sngags pa la /
T02TD1193E:28b-33: 'di zhes bya ba'i phyag rgya long //
T02TD1193E:28b-35: gal te sems byang nas dngos grub tu gyur ma khad nas /
T02TD1193E:28b-36: rang la phyag rgya med pa la 'byor pa rnams kyis ming 'di zhes bya ba ni byag rgya ston pas na /
T02TD1193E:28b-37: de rtog pa med par blangs la sgrub ces pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:28b-38: bdag nyid mthu yis brtags nas kyang //
T02TD1193E:28b-39: longs spyod phyir ni spyod min bshad //
T02TD1193E:28b-41: bdag gi sems sbyangs pa dang /
T02TD1193E:28b-42: rtog pa zad cing man ngag thob pas sgrub kyi /
T02TD1193E:28b-43: 'dod pa'i longs spyod kyi phyir spyod pa ni ma yin no //
T02TD1193E:28b-44: gal te 'dod pa'i phyir spyod na ni /
T02TD1193E:29a-2: sems can dmyal ba la sogs par skye ba'i don /
T02TD1193E:29a-3: rnam par snang mdzad sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgya cher 'grel pa las kyang /
T02TD1193E:29a-4: gzhan du 'dod pa'i longs spyod la //
T02TD1193E:29a-5: mngon par 'dod pa skyes gyur na //
T02TD1193E:29a-6: ma goms dbang gis sngags pa ni //
T02TD1193E:29a-9: gzhung gzhan la ni phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i grogs rig pa de dang /
T02TD1193E:29a-10: bdag sgrub pa po gnyi ga yang dbang dang dam tshig tu ldan pa /
T02TD1193E:29a-11: sems shin tu byang ba man ngag thob pa rnams kyis mchod cing bsgrubs na /
T02TD1193E:29a-13: gzhan dag gis tshig tsam du bzlas te /
T02TD1193E:29a-14: gzu lums su spyad na bdag kyang ngan 'gro la sogs pa rnams su brlag la /
T02TD1193E:29a-15: gzhan yang phung bar byed pa yin pas na /
T02TD1193E:29a-16: tshul bzhin du sgrub cing mchod ces pa'i don /
T02TD1193E:29a-18: bdag med rnal 'byor ma sbyor ba //
T02TD1193E:29a-19: phyag rgya rnams kyi khyad par ni //
T02TD1193E:29a-20: phyag rgya phyag rgya gnyis pa'o //
T02TD1193E:29a-22: bdag med pa la spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1193E:29a-23: thabs med par shes rab gcig pu la mi 'grub la /
T02TD1193E:29a-24: shes rab med par yang thabs kyis mi 'grub ste /
T02TD1193E:29a-25: de bas na de gnyis bstan pa las phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub 'byung bas na /
T02TD1193E:29a-26: phyag rgya phyag rgya gnyis po zhes bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:29a-27: 'o na gong du lha mo 'ba' zhig gis dkyil 'khor la ji ltar dngos grub skye zhe na /
T02TD1193E:29a-29: bud med gzugs ni spangs nas kyang //
T02TD1193E:29a-30: bcom ldan gzugs ni gzhan byas te //
T02TD1193E:29a-31: zhes pa la lha mo'i gzugs spangs nas thabs kyi gzugs su bya ba ste /
T02TD1193E:29a-32: de yi phyag rgya ma gnyis spangs te padma'i sgor sbyar bas rdo rjer gyur la /
T02TD1193E:29a-33: cig shos kyis sgre'ur gyur te /
T02TD1193E:29a-34: ngos gnyis su ni dril bu yis //
T02TD1193E:29a-36: de nas gzugs ril gyis he ru kar gyur pa'i don /
T02TD1193E:29a-37: de lta bu'i thabs kyis bsgrubs na dngos grub tu 'gyur ba'i tha tshig go //
T02TD1193E:29a-38: des yon tan ni sgrub cing chos na /
T02TD1193E:29a-39: skye ba dang 'jig pa las grol te /
T02TD1193E:29a-40: shes rab thabs kyis gnon mi nus //
T02TD1193E:29a-42: de bas na thabs kyis ni skye ba'i 'khor ba med par byed la /
T02TD1193E:29a-43: shes rab kyis ni 'jigs pa'i 'khor ba las rgal bas /
T02TD1193E:29a-44: srid mthar byed ces pa'i don /
T02TD1193E:29b-0: des na 'jigs pa med cing skye ba med pa @29b de ltar thabs dang shes rab gnyis las grub pas ni /
T02TD1193E:29b-1: dngos po 'khor ba skye ba dang mthun pa las thar te /
T02TD1193E:29b-2: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas grub ces pa'i tha tshig go //
T02TD1193E:29b-3: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i sbyor bas ni bya ba nas /
T02TD1193E:29b-4: rtag tu sbyor ba byas pa yin //
T02TD1193E:29b-5: zhes bya ba'i bar ni bskyed pa'i rim pa dngos po skye ba ther zug tu rtog pa sel te /
T02TD1193E:29b-6: tshig gi don ni rgyud las gsal bar ma bris so //
T02TD1193E:29b-7: da ni dbang bskur ba'i thabs bstan te /
T02TD1193E:29b-8: bde ba nag po la sogs pa ni /
T02TD1193E:29b-9: dngos po thams cad bde ba chen po las logs na med ces bstan pa'o //
T02TD1193E:29b-10: rdo rje snying pos gsol pa zhes bya ba ni sdud pa po'i tshig go //
T02TD1193E:29b-11: bcom ldan bde chen mchog dam las thams cad 'byung na /
T02TD1193E:29b-12: bskyed pa'i rim pa gong du bstan pas ci zhig bgyi zhes zhus pa la bka' stsal pa /
T02TD1193E:29b-13: dad pa'i shugs can khyod bden mi bden yang /
T02TD1193E:29b-14: bskyed pa'i rim pa la ma brten par /
T02TD1193E:29b-15: rdzogs pa'i rim pa logs na med de /
T02TD1193E:29b-17: dngos med lus las bde ba gang //
T02TD1193E:29b-18: bde ba ngag gis brjod mi nus //
T02TD1193E:29b-19: gzugs can khyab pas khyab pa yi //
T02TD1193E:29b-20: 'gro ba rnams ni bde bas khyab //
T02TD1193E:29b-22: bde ba ni lus la brten nas skye'i /
T02TD1193E:29b-23: dngos po med pa las ni ma yin no //
T02TD1193E:29b-24: de bas na 'gro ba rnams ni bde bas khyab //
T02TD1193E:29b-25: ces bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
T02TD1193E:29b-26: gang yang le los zil non bya ba ni /
T02TD1193E:29b-27: de lta'i bde ba chen po ni le lo can sems rnam par g-yeng ba /
T02TD1193E:29b-28: 'du 'dzi'i dbang du gyur pas mi rtog pa'i don /
T02TD1193E:29b-29: gru gsum chos kyi phyag rgya de ni /
T02TD1193E:29b-30: sangs rgyas la sogs pa sa bcu'i khyad par gyi yon tan dpag tu med pa skye bas na /
T02TD1193E:29b-31: rin chen za ma tog ces bya'o //
T02TD1193E:29b-32: mthar thug dga' ba'i rang ngo bo /
T02TD1193E:29b-34: gsum pa spangs pa'i dga' ba'o //
T02TD1193E:29b-36: shin tu dga' ba rnams ni goms pa las /
T02TD1193E:29b-37: dper na mun par sgron ma bteg na shin tu gsal ba ltar /
T02TD1193E:29b-38: dga' ba'i snang bas dngos po la rnam par rtog pa'i mun pa bsal nas /
T02TD1193E:29b-39: mchog gi dngos grub thob ces bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:29b-40: gsal byed kyang ni de bzhin no //
T02TD1193E:29b-42: dga' ba rnams kyis grub pa thob pa ltar /
T02TD1193E:29b-43: a'a li k'a li yi ge rnams las kyang //
T02TD1193E:29b-44: dngos grub 'byung zhes pa'i tha tshig go //
T02TD1193E:30a-1: dpe don rnams ni brda phrang sla'o //
T02TD1193E:30a-4: 'dod chags 'khrig pas 'khor bar 'ching ba rnams ni /
T02TD1193E:30a-5: man ngag bla ma la bsnyen bkur byas pas thob nas /
T02TD1193E:30a-6: dga' ba rnams ltar spyad pas /
T02TD1193E:30a-7: 'dod chags 'khor bar skye ba'i me 'dod chags rnam par dag pa /
T02TD1193E:30a-8: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyis zhi ste /
T02TD1193E:30a-9: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub tu 'gyur zhes pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:30a-10: de su'i spyod yul yin zhe na /
T02TD1193E:30a-11: zlog pa'i brtag pa 'di nyid ni //
T02TD1193E:30a-12: sangs rgyas mu stegs can gyis min //
T02TD1193E:30a-14: dngos po nyan thos kyi rigs can lta ba dang /
T02TD1193E:30a-15: spyod pa dman pa la mos pa dngos grub chen po la rgyab kyis phyogs pa rnams kyi yul ma yin zhes bya ba'i don /
T02TD1193E:30a-16: 'byung ba rang gzugs lnga pa ni //
T02TD1193E:30a-17: bde ba chen po lnga ru 'gyur //
T02TD1193E:30a-19: bde ba chen po zla ba zhu ba la /
T02TD1193E:30a-20: 'byung ba lnga tshang la de la bde ba lnga zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:30a-21: lnga bo rnams kyang bde ba'i dngos po ni gcig las med ces pa'i tha tshig go //
T02TD1193E:30a-22: shes rab thabs kyi sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1193E:30a-23: bya ba la sogs pa la shes rab dang thabs snyoms par 'jug pa'i skad cig ma la /
T02TD1193E:30a-26: rigs rnam pa lnga la sogs pa /
T02TD1193E:30a-27: skad cig ma'i tshul gyis rdzogs pa ni ci rigs par shes par bya'o //
T02TD1193E:30a-30: // / da ni le'u gsum pa'i bshad ba ston te /
T02TD1193E:30a-31: rgyud thams cad kyi rtog pa brjod pa zhes bya ba ni /
T02TD1193E:30a-32: thabs kyi rgyud dpal gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs pa dang /
T02TD1193E:30a-33: shes rab kyi rgyud nges par brjod pa bla ma'i rgyud la sogs pa thams cad kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
T02TD1193E:30a-34: man ngag gsal bar ston zhes pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:30a-35: de las khyad par du rnal 'byor ma ste /
T02TD1193E:30a-36: shes rab kyi rgyud mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog ces bya ba la sogs pa'i rgyud thams cad gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir ro //
T02TD1193E:30a-38: dbang bskur ba la sogs pa ston pas na /
T02TD1193E:30a-39: de la sdom pa bshad par bya //
T02TD1193E:30a-41: sdom pa sangs rgyas thams cad de //
T02TD1193E:30a-42: ae wam la ni rab tu bzhugs //
T02TD1193E:30a-44: rnam pa'i sdom pa ni sangs rgyas thams cad de /
T02TD1193E:30a-45: sangs rgyas ni ae wam la 'dus te /
T02TD1193E:30b-2: byin du ni byang chub kyi sems yin te /
T02TD1193E:30b-3: sems de bha ga la bzhugs zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:30b-4: de yang dngos su sgrub pa po dang /
T02TD1193E:30b-6: bsgrub par bya ba gsum dgongs pa'i don gyis bshad pa ste /
T02TD1193E:30b-7: sgrub pa po ni rnal 'byor pa /
T02TD1193E:30b-8: rang nyid longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i bdag nyid pa yin la /
T02TD1193E:30b-10: chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid ae yin la /
T02TD1193E:30b-11: bsgrub par bya ba ni gnyis su med pa'i ye shes te /
T02TD1193E:30b-13: de lta bu'i man ngag slob dpon gyis phog cing dbang bskur ba la bde ba chen po gcig pu byed ces bya'o //
T02TD1193E:30b-14: gang 'di ae ni sna tshogs sku //
T02TD1193E:30b-15: zhes bya ba la yi ge ae ste /
T02TD1193E:30b-16: mkha' de nyid thams cad kyi bdag nyid du gyur pa /
T02TD1193E:30b-17: chos kyi dbyings kyi ngo bo nyid do //
T02TD1193E:30b-18: dbus su wam gyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1193E:30b-20: mkha' de'i dbus su wam ste thabs dang byang chub kyi sems gnas zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:30b-21: sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog / ces pa la /
T02TD1193E:30b-22: sangs rgyas kyang yin la rin po che yang yin pas na rin chen no //
T02TD1193E:30b-23: za ma tog ltar mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa'am /
T02TD1193E:30b-24: gzhal yas khang gi yon tan dam pa dang ldan pas sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog ste /
T02TD1193E:30b-25: dngos su phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rin po che ste /
T02TD1193E:30b-26: che ba'i yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung gnas zhes bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:30b-27: gnas der ni bde ba dang dga' ba thams cad kyi bdag nyid yin pas na /
T02TD1193E:30b-28: de las skyes zhes bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:30b-29: skad cig dbye ba'i khyad par can //
T02TD1193E:30b-31: mthar thug pa'i ye shes skad cig ma ni /
T02TD1193E:30b-32: gong ma'i ae wam las skyes pas na /
T02TD1193E:30b-33: ae wam la ni rab tu gnas //
T02TD1193E:30b-34: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
T02TD1193E:30b-35: de yang rnam pa sna tshogs zhes bya ba la sogs pa bzhi pos ston to //
T02TD1193E:30b-36: 'dir rnam pa sna tshogs pa la sogs pa bzhi dang /
T02TD1193E:30b-37: dga' ba rnam pa bzhi dang /
T02TD1193E:30b-38: dbang bskur ba rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa /
T02TD1193E:30b-39: man ngag gi gnas chen po bcu gnyis la sogs pa ni bla ma'i bka' las shes par bya'o //
T02TD1193E:30b-40: rdo rje snying pos gsol ba /
T02TD1193E:30b-41: dam tshig rnams ni gang la gnas //
T02TD1193E:30b-42: sdom pa rnams ni gang zhig yin //
T02TD1193E:30b-43: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
T02TD1193E:30b-44: khyod kyis srog chags gsad par bya //
T02TD1193E:31a-1: gyi tshig kyang smra bar bya //
T02TD1193E:31a-2: khyod kyis ma byin blang bar bya //
T02TD1193E:31a-3: gzhan gyi bud med bsten par gyis //
T02TD1193E:31a-4: zhes bya ba la sogs pa smos pa la /
T02TD1193E:31a-5: 'dir gang zag kha cig gis sgra ji bzhin du bzung ste /
T02TD1193E:31a-6: srog gcod pa la sogs pa log par spyod pa yod de srog gcod pa ni rang bzhin gyis kha na ma tho ba rnams kyi nang na yang ches rags pa yin zhing /
T02TD1193E:31a-7: ngan song gi rgyu'i gtso bor gsungs pa dang /
T02TD1193E:31a-8: mi dge pa chen po yin zhing ston pa'i bstan pa la 'gal ba'i rtsa ba yin te /
T02TD1193E:31a-9: de bas na bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' mtha' dag las srog gcod pa mi 'byung bar shes par bya'o //
T02TD1193E:31a-10: srog gcod pa ni mu stegs kyi chos kha cig las 'byung ste /
T02TD1193E:31a-11: sngon bram ze sha la dga' ba dag cig gis sha 'dod pa'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:31a-12: ri dags dang phyugs la sogs pa'i gzugs brnyan byas nas gzhan gyi mig brid de /
T02TD1193E:31a-13: tha mar phyugs dngos su gsod cing de nyid lhar skye bar 'gyur ro zhes gzhung sgrub pa dag la /
T02TD1193E:31a-14: mu stegs gzhan gtsang mar spyod pa brtul zhugs la gnas pa bsam gtan la 'jog pa dag chos ma yin par 'dod de /
T02TD1193E:31a-15: de yang drang srong rgyas pas rang gi bu bram ze khye'u ne tso mchod sbyin la btsud pa dang /
T02TD1193E:31a-16: ne tsos pha la 'di skad du /
T02TD1193E:31a-17: mchod sdong btsugs pas phyugs bsad de //
T02TD1193E:31a-18: khrag gi dam tshig byas gyur pa //
T02TD1193E:31a-21: zhes bya ba la sogs pa smras pas /
T02TD1193E:31a-22: sun phyung bar gyur to zhes grags na /
T02TD1193E:31a-23: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la zhugs pa rnams kyis /
T02TD1193E:31a-24: de la chos dang ldan pa'i lam zhes ji ltar bgrang //
T02TD1193E:31a-25: gsang ba 'dus pa'i 'grel pa slob dpon dpal gyi sdes mdzad pa las /
T02TD1193E:31a-26: de la srog gcod pa zhes bya ba na /
T02TD1193E:31a-27: ye shes kyi rdo rjes sems can gyi khams ma lus pa mi dmigs par byed pa'i stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin thob par byed pa de gang yin pa de /
T02TD1193E:31a-28: 'dir srog gcod pa zhes bshad pa dang /
T02TD1193E:31a-29: de yang de nyid kyi t'i k'a las kyang /
T02TD1193E:31a-30: srog ces bya ba rlung chen po rtag tu 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid can te /
T02TD1193E:31a-31: bkag cing bsdams pa la ni srog gcod pa zhes bya'i /
T02TD1193E:31a-32: sems can bsad pa ni ma yin no zhes 'byung ste /
T02TD1193E:31b-0: des na 'di'i don kyang srog dang rtsol ba @31b bsdams nas /
T02TD1193E:31b-1: sems nang du bsdus te mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par 'jog pa ni srog gcod pa zhes bya'o zhes dgongs so //
T02TD1193E:31b-2: gsang ba 'dus pa'i dka' 'grel slob dpon kun dga' snying pos mdzad pa las kyang /
T02TD1193E:31b-3: de la ye shes kyi rdo rjes sems can gyi khams ma lus pa dngos po med par byed pa'i stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin thob pa'i don ni srog gcod pa'o zhes gsungs so //
T02TD1193E:31b-4: gsang ba 'dus pa'i 'grel pa sgron ma gsal bar byed pa las kyang /
T02TD1193E:31b-5: sems can thams cad bsad na ni //
T02TD1193E:31b-7: stong pa nyid du bya bas rnam par bshig pa'o zhes bshad pa dang /
T02TD1193E:31b-8: dgongs pa lung bstan pa'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:31b-9: gang gis phung sogs dngos med pa //
T02TD1193E:31b-10: zhi gnas las kyang sems kyis byas //
T02TD1193E:31b-11: de ni srog gcod byed pa ste //
T02TD1193E:31b-12: theg pa'i mchog la gnas pa yin //
T02TD1193E:31b-14: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa zhes bya ba'i rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:31b-15: rdo rje gsang ba 'di lta bus //
T02TD1193E:31b-16: sems can thams cad bsad na ni //
T02TD1193E:31b-17: mi bskyod sangs rgyas zhing dag tu //
T02TD1193E:31b-18: rgyal ba'i sras su skye bar 'gyur //
T02TD1193E:31b-20: bshad ma thag pa'i stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis /
T02TD1193E:31b-21: bdag gzhan gyi rgyud du gtogs pa'i 'jig tshogs la lta ba la sogs pa rnam par bshig ste /
T02TD1193E:31b-22: ma skyes par bsgom pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:31b-23: 'bras bu gsungs pa ni mi bskyod pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du skye ba'o //
T02TD1193E:31b-24: de bas na bsam gtan gyi sbyor ba 'dis sku dang gsung dang thugs mi dmigs pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi ting nge 'dzin bsgoms na /
T02TD1193E:31b-25: mi bskyod pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du skye bar 'gyur ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:31b-26: la la dag ni srog gcod pa ni sems can 'khor ba las bsgral pa yin no zhes rtogs na /
T02TD1193E:31b-27: de lta bu ma yin te /
T02TD1193E:31b-28: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed de /
T02TD1193E:31b-29: tshogs dpag tu med par bsags nas /
T02TD1193E:31b-30: sems can thams cad 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las byang chub kyi skam la 'don pa ni sgrol ba zhes bya'i /
T02TD1193E:31b-31: gsod pa la ni mi bya ste /
T02TD1193E:31b-32: gal te sems can bsad pas 'khor ba las bsgral bar nus na ni /
T02TD1193E:32a-0: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' mthu bo che rnams kyis gsod pa'i sbyor ba 'ba' zhig gis sems can gyi don mdzad pa'i @32a * //
T02TD1193E:32a-2: rnam pa de lta bu gang nas kyang ma gsungs /
T02TD1193E:32a-4: bsgral ba'i tshig gis don yang gsod pa ma yin no //
T02TD1193E:32a-5: de bas na srog gcod pa dang 'brel pa dang 'di la chos su bgrang ba ni /
T02TD1193E:32a-6: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa mtha' dag dang 'gal ba nyid yin pas /
T02TD1193E:32a-7: byang chub kyi lam du mi rung ngo //
T02TD1193E:32a-8: spros pas chog gi dkyus ma nyid la 'jug par bya'o //
T02TD1193E:32a-9: de bas na rgyud nyid las /
T02TD1193E:32a-10: srog ni sems zhes bshad pa ste //
T02TD1193E:32a-11: gcig pa'i sems ni srog bcad yin //
T02TD1193E:32a-13: bdag gi sems 'od gsal ba dang /
T02TD1193E:32a-14: sems can thams cad kyi sems dang chos thams cad shes rab kyi mtshon gyis skye ba med par shes pa ni srog gcod pa zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:32a-15: brdzun gyi chig tu smra ba la sogs pa rang bzhin gyis kha na ma tho ba yin pa'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:32a-16: 'phags pa'i lam dang 'gal ba yin pa dang /
T02TD1193E:32a-17: dngos po brdzun smra ba ni ma yin no //
T02TD1193E:32a-18: snod dang bcud kyis bsdus pa'i phyi nang gi chos thams cad ni byed pa pos byas pa ma yin zhing /
T02TD1193E:32a-19: rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba sgyu ma lta bu rgyu rkyen la rag las pa slu ba'i chos can yin par ston pa ni brdzun du smra ba'o //
T02TD1193E:32a-20: de yang dgongs pa lung bstan pa'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:32a-21: nang dang de bzhin phyi rol dag ;
T02TD1193E:32a-22: / rten 'byung gnyis su ston pa ni /
T02TD1193E:32a-23: de ni brdzun smra dga' ba ste //
T02TD1193E:32a-24: gnas med la gnas rnal 'byor pa'o //
T02TD1193E:32a-25: zhes smras pa ni brdzun du smra ba'o //
T02TD1193E:32a-26: sems can gyi khams thams cad sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin du bskyed par bsgoms pas /
T02TD1193E:32a-27: sems can gyi khams ma lus pa'i sems dang sems las byung ba'i rnam par rtog pa'i rdzas phrogs shing gsal ba ni /
T02TD1193E:32a-29: de yang dgongs pa lung bstan pa'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:32a-30: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi ye shes gang //
T02TD1193E:32a-31: de ni rjes su shes bya ste //
T02TD1193E:32a-32: de phrogs ngang tshul gang yin pa //
T02TD1193E:32a-33: gzhan gyi nor la chags par 'dod //
T02TD1193E:32a-34: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kyi rdul phra rab dang mnyam pa'i lha mo thams cad dang yang dag par mnyam par sbyor ba'i bsgom pa ni rtag tu 'dod pa la dga' ba'o //
T02TD1193E:32b-0: bud med mchog ni bcom ldan 'das yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa de @32b bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yum du gyur pa /
T02TD1193E:32b-1: mtshan gyi rnam pa gzhan yang phyag rgya chen po zhes bya ba yin te /
T02TD1193E:32b-2: de dag dang gcig tu 'dres par gyur pa la dgongs nas /
T02TD1193E:32b-3: gzhan gyi bud med bsten par gsungs pa yin no //
T02TD1193E:32b-4: gang zhig de nyid dngos gcig pa //
T02TD1193E:32b-5: de bzhin nyid la rtag sbyor ba //
T02TD1193E:32b-6: sems can de de 'dod la dga' //
T02TD1193E:32b-7: sgrub pa'i mchog la dam par 'gyur //
T02TD1193E:32b-9: de bas na rgyud 'di nyid las kyang 'jig rten bsgral bar bya zhes pa /
T02TD1193E:32b-10: brdzun gyi sgrar yang brjod pa yin //
T02TD1193E:32b-11: btsun mo'i shu kra ma byin len //
T02TD1193E:32b-12: gzhan gyi bud med rang gi lha mo //
T02TD1193E:32b-14: srog gcod pa la sogs pa'i tshig 'di rnams ni dgongs pas gsungs pa yin pas na /
T02TD1193E:32b-15: sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:32b-16: lhag ma ni brda phrad par sla bas ma bris so //
T02TD1193E:32b-17: dpa' bo thams cad bza' bar bya //
T02TD1193E:32b-18: zhes pa la gtsang btsog bzang ngan kun mnyam par bza' ba'i don /
T02TD1193E:32b-19: kha dog lnga ni mnyam par spyad //
T02TD1193E:32b-20: ces bya ba ni rgyal rigs dang bram ze dang rje'u rigs dang rigs ngan dang dombi'i rigs so //
T02TD1193E:32b-21: bdud rtsi lnga dang bu ram chang //
T02TD1193E:32b-23: bdud rtsi lnga ni rdzas lnga yin no //
T02TD1193E:32b-25: chang gi dug ni mig la sogs pa'i dbang po'i dri ma'o //
T02TD1193E:32b-38: de dag mi rtog bza' bar bya //
T02TD1193E:32b-40: sna tshogs ri bo'i gos bgos shing //
T02TD1193E:32b-42: ro'i gos las kha dog mang po can gyi smad kyi dbang po 'gegs pa'i gos la bya ba'i don /
T02TD1193E:32b-44: thal chen gyis lus bskus pa la bya ba'o //
T02TD1193E:32b-45: yi dags gnas las skyes pa'i me tog ni ro la bcings pa'i me tog gi phreng ba bor ba de mgo la bcing ba'i tha tshig go //
T02TD1193E:32b-46: lhag ma ni brda phrad sla bas ma bris so //
T02TD1193E:32b-47: ka li ka ni sangs rgyas lnga //
T02TD1193E:32b-48: zhes bya ba la sogs pa ni //
T02TD1193E:32b-49: de nyid mthar thug dga' ba ste //
T02TD1193E:32b-50: lhag ma ni ci rigs par shes par bya'o //
T02TD1193E:32b-53: // / da ni le'u bzhi pa bshad do /
T02TD1193E:33a-1: dang brda la sogs pa ston to //
T02TD1193E:33a-2: glu dang gar ni gnyis po yis //
T02TD1193E:33a-3: gar mchog glu ni blang bar bya //
T02TD1193E:33a-5: glu ni aa mi ta pa'i gzugs kyis blangs la gar ni he ru ka'i gzugs kyis bya'o //
T02TD1193E:33a-6: sgog skya'i dri la sogs pa ni grub pa thob par gyur ba'i mtshan ma ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-8: / ga bur la sogs pa'i dri zhim po 'byung ba'o //
T02TD1193E:33a-9: de bzhin dang pa la sogs pa'i sgra dang /
T02TD1193E:33a-10: ce sbyang ni ku zhes zer ro //
T02TD1193E:33a-11: phyag rgya'i mtshan ma ni rgyud las gsal lo //
T02TD1193E:33a-12: mi shes sgrub pos dngos mi 'grub //
T02TD1193E:33a-14: zhe sdang la sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
T02TD1193E:33a-15: rigs rnam pa ldang sbyar te sgrub pa ni /
T02TD1193E:33a-16: de dag gi rigs mthun par sbyar ba ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-17: dper na rims sel ba'i sngags la /
T02TD1193E:33a-18: rims kyi sngags zer ba dang 'dra bar /
T02TD1193E:33a-19: de dag gi gnyen por gyur pa'i ye shes gang yin pa de la de skad ces bya ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-20: de bas na chos mthun pa'i tshul ltar na /
T02TD1193E:33a-21: phung po lnga dang tshul mthun pa'i chos kyi sgos nyon mongs pa lnga rnam par dag pa ni rigs lngar snang ba yin te /
T02TD1193E:33a-22: yod pa dang med pa dang /
T02TD1193E:33a-23: rtag pa dang chad pa dang /
T02TD1193E:33a-24: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa la sogs pa gnyis su dmigs pa'i shes pa la sdang zhing 'joms pas na zhe sdang ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-25: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes so //
T02TD1193E:33a-26: de'i phyir zhe sdang rnam par dag pa ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-27: mi bskyod pa ni bdag med zhe sdang phyag rgya ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-29: 'di ltar gti mug ni rmongs shing bye brag mi phyed pa'i mtshan nyid can yin pa ltar /
T02TD1193E:33a-30: chos kyi dbyings la nges par rtogs pa'i ye shes kyang chos thams cad ro gcig par rtog pa nyid kyis bye brag mi 'byed par cha mthun pas na /
T02TD1193E:33a-31: bems po ltar gnas pa'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:33a-32: gti mug rnam par dag pa ni rnam par snang mdzad de /
T02TD1193E:33a-33: dngos su rdo rje gti mug phyag rgya yin //
T02TD1193E:33a-34: zhes bya ba dang sbyar ro //
T02TD1193E:33a-35: phrag dog ni gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa la mi bzod cing /
T02TD1193E:33a-36: bdag nyid 'byor pa dang ldan par 'dod pa'o //
T02TD1193E:33a-37: 'dir ni 'gro ba'i don gzhan la ltos pa med par bdag nyid gcig pus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa byed 'dod pa ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-38: las kyi mtshan nyid phrag dog rnam par dag pa ni don yod grub pa ste /
T02TD1193E:33a-39: dngos su goo r'i phrag dog phyag rgya ste //
T02TD1193E:33b-0: 'dod chags ni dngos po gang yang rung ba la chags shing zhen pa'i @33b mtshan nyid can yin la /
T02TD1193E:33b-1: sems can thams cad smin cing grol ba la chags pa'am /
T02TD1193E:33b-2: yang dag pa'i don la zhen cing mi gtong ba ni 'dod chags pa ste /
T02TD1193E:33b-3: de ni 'dod chags rnam par dag pa'i ngo bo 'od dpag tu med pa ste /
T02TD1193E:33b-4: dngos su ba r'i 'dod chags phyag rgya yin //
T02TD1193E:33b-6: nga rgyal ni rlom sems kyi bdag nyid yin la sangs rgyas thams cad dang bdag nyid mnyam par rtog pa'i dbang gis nga rgyal rnam par dag pa ni rin chen 'byung ldan te /
T02TD1193E:33b-8: dngos su ser sna'i phyag na mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1193E:33b-10: de bas na 'khor ba'i spyod yul nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin can gyi 'dod chags la sogs pa la brten pa la mi bya'i /
T02TD1193E:33b-11: 'dir chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa la sogs pa khong du chud pa'i gnyen pos snga ma'i rang bzhin dang bral te /
T02TD1193E:33b-12: rtogs pa'i khyad par gzhan skye ba ni /
T02TD1193E:33b-13: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos kyi sgor gyur te /
T02TD1193E:33b-14: dper na dug sngags grub pas dug gi nus pa med par byas te /
T02TD1193E:33b-15: dug bsten pas sman du gyur pa'i nus pa gzhan skyes pa dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:33b-16: 'di skad du gsungs pa yin gyi gzhan du na 'di dag 'khor ba'i rgyu ma tshang ba med pa yin zhing /
T02TD1193E:33b-17: ngan song la sogs par 'dren pa'i dug nyid yin pas /
T02TD1193E:33b-18: rgyu dang 'bras bu phyin ci log tu gyur pa ni 'gal ba nyid yin pa'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:33b-19: 'di dag bsten pa las rnam par dag pa'i ye shes 'byung zhing 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur ba mi srid do //
T02TD1193E:33b-20: de'i phyir spros pa med pa'i shes rab stobs su gyur pa dug sngags grub pa lta bus zin na /
T02TD1193E:33b-21: gdod thabs kyi dam par 'gyur gyi gzhan du ni ma yin no //
T02TD1193E:33b-22: de ltar na nyon mongs pa de rnams kyi gnyen po dang /
T02TD1193E:33b-23: de rnam par dag pa'i ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin las rigs lnga'i khyad par du snang ba yin pas na /
T02TD1193E:33b-25: sangs rgyas thams cad chags las 'khrungs //
T02TD1193E:33b-26: de bzhin rmongs dang sdang las 'khrungs //
T02TD1193E:33b-28: dpal mchog dang po'i rgyud las kyang /
T02TD1193E:33b-29: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum //
T02TD1193E:33b-31: dug nyid nye bar zhi gyur na //
T02TD1193E:33b-32: dug ni dug med byas pa yin //
T02TD1193E:33b-34: dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i mdo las kyang /
T02TD1193E:34a-0: 'od srungs 'di lta ste dper na sngags dang sman gyis yongs su zin @34a * //
T02TD1193E:34a-1: pa'i dug gis 'chi bar byed mi nus so //
T02TD1193E:34a-2: 'od srungs de bzhin du ye shes dang thabs mkhas pas yongs su zin pa'i dug gis kyang /
T02TD1193E:34a-3: log par ltung bar byed mi nus she'o //
T02TD1193E:34a-4: de ltar nyon mongs pa lnga po'i rnam par dag pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa lnga ston par mdzad pa 'di yang bde bar gshegs pa'i thabs mkhas pa nyid yin gyi /
T02TD1193E:34a-5: nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa ni ma yin no //
T02TD1193E:34a-7: gang gi rang bzhin chags dang rnam bral yang //
T02TD1193E:34a-8: gdul bya'i don phyir khro la khro ba dang //
T02TD1193E:34a-9: 'dod chags can la chags pa ltar ston pa //
T02TD1193E:34a-10: byang chub mchog gnas de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1193E:34a-12: yang 'di ltar bcom ldan 'das ni bag chags dang bas pa'i nyon mongs pa yongs su spangs pa'i mthar byon pa yin du zin kyang /
T02TD1193E:34a-13: gdul bya kha cig gi dbang du mdzad nas /
T02TD1193E:34a-14: btsun mo'i tshogs la sogs pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lha mo rnams kyis yongs su bskor te /
T02TD1193E:34a-15: bzhugs nas 'dod pa la sogs nye bar longs spyod pa lta bur ston par mdzad pa yang /
T02TD1193E:34a-16: ci zhig las dgongs te de ltar mdzad ce na /
T02TD1193E:34a-17: 'dod pa'i dbang phyug la sogs pa'i lha rnams bdag nyid kyi chung ma dang slas kyi tshogs pa 'dod pa'i longs spyod kyis shin tu dregs shing /
T02TD1193E:34a-18: rang las mchog tu gyur pa gzhan med par rtogs pa dag gi dregs pa bsal nas /
T02TD1193E:34a-19: bstan pa la gzud par bya ba'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi yon tan tshad med pa rnam pa bzhi dang /
T02TD1193E:34a-20: pha rol tu phyin pa drug la sogs pa lha mo'i bdag nyid du sprul pa mdzad nas /
T02TD1193E:34a-21: lha las ches khyad par du gyur pa'i 'dod pa'i longs spyod dang ldan par bstan pa des /
T02TD1193E:34a-22: de mthong nas rang gi 'khor ba shin tu yid byung zhing nga rgyal med pa'i sgo nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i phun sum tshogs la 'dod pa skye bar 'gyur te /
T02TD1193E:34a-23: de dag thabs gang gis thob par 'gyur zhes zhus pa dang /
T02TD1193E:34a-24: de thob pa'i thabs su gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
T02TD1193E:34a-25: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa la sogs pa la btsud pas /
T02TD1193E:34a-26: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i yon tan de dag thob par mdzad pa yin no //
T02TD1193E:34a-27: yang dam tshig chen po'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:34b-0: @34b rtag tu 'dod pa gnas pa yi //
T02TD1193E:34b-1: lha yi bu ni 'di rnams dang //
T02TD1193E:34b-2: 'dod chags can ni gzhan gyi phyir //
T02TD1193E:34b-3: rab dga'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa yin //
T02TD1193E:34b-5: 'di ni khyi gus khyi gu 'byin pa 'dra bar /
T02TD1193E:34b-6: skye bo 'dod chags kyi shas che ba la /
T02TD1193E:34b-7: 'dod chags sdong ba'i phyir shin tu khyad par du 'phags pa'i btsun mo'i tshogs dang /
T02TD1193E:34b-8: 'dod pa'i yul la spyod pa lta bur ston pa mdzad de /
T02TD1193E:34b-9: de tha mal pa'i 'dod pa la skyo ba bskyed cing /
T02TD1193E:34b-10: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bla na med pa'i 'byor pa la sems 'dun cing 'dod pa bskyed pa dang /
T02TD1193E:34b-11: de dag gi rang bzhin rtog par mdzad pas /
T02TD1193E:34b-12: de la zhen cing ma dang mar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral bas /
T02TD1193E:34b-13: rim gyis nyon mongs pa las grol zhing yon tan gyi tshogs rdzogs par mdzad pa yin no //
T02TD1193E:34b-14: de bas na rdo rje dra ba'i rgyud las /
T02TD1193E:34b-15: 'gro ba 'dod chags kyis ni rmongs pa la //
T02TD1193E:34b-16: 'dod chags mi yis sel bar byed pa yin ;
T02TD1193E:34b-18: 'dir 'dod chags kyi rnam par dag pa rgya cher gsungs pa ni /
T02TD1193E:34b-19: mngal nas skye ba gdul ba'i phyir dang /
T02TD1193E:34b-20: rgyud 'di las shes rab dang snyoms par 'jug pa 'ba' zhig ston pa'i phyir /
T02TD1193E:34b-21: dgongs pa'i dbang gis de ltar ston par mdzad pa yin la /
T02TD1193E:34b-22: de bzhin gshegs pas 'dod chags dang bcas par rtog cing /
T02TD1193E:34b-23: tshul dang mi mthun par 'dzin pa ste /
T02TD1193E:34b-24: de dag gis dgongs pa ma rtogs pa yin gyi /
T02TD1193E:34b-25: 'di ni 'gro ba gdul ba'i phyir thabs kyis mdzad pa nyid yin no //
T02TD1193E:34b-26: de yang 'jig rten dang rjes su mthun par 'jug pas /
T02TD1193E:34b-27: mar me mdzad nas bzung nas ni //
T02TD1193E:34b-28: de bzhin gshegs pa 'dod chags bral //
T02TD1193E:34b-29: sgra gcan zin la sras zhes gsungs //
T02TD1193E:34b-33: dkyus pa nyid la 'jug par bya ste /
T02TD1193E:34b-34: pukka s'i ni zhe sdang rgya //
T02TD1193E:34b-36: lhag ma rnams ni 'bad pas spang bar bya //
T02TD1193E:34b-38: rtsa gsum pa ni mchog yin gyi //
T02TD1193E:34b-39: lhag ma ni rtsa nyi shu rtsa dgu dgos med zer ro //
T02TD1193E:34b-41: bcu drug cha ni gang yang mi dgos te /
T02TD1193E:35a-0: bcu drug cha ni nyi shu rtsa dgu las phra ba'i rtsa ni sus kyang mi rtogs shing las gang yang mi nus @35a * //
T02TD1193E:35a-3: gzhi'i don gyi bya ba mi byed pa'i phyir zhes 'byung bas so //
T02TD1193E:35a-4: byang chub sems rgyun zla ba ste //
T02TD1193E:35a-5: bco lnga'i cha ni bdag nyid can //
T02TD1193E:35a-7: zla ba tshes bco lnga pa'i mtshan nyid lha byang chub kyi sems yin te /
T02TD1193E:35a-8: de ni bde ba chen po'i bdag nyid can yin pas na /
T02TD1193E:35a-9: dngos su rnal 'byor ma ldan pas rtogs kyi /
T02TD1193E:35a-10: thabs gcig pus ni mi rtogs pa'i don to //
T02TD1193E:35a-11: bde ba yis ni bsrungs pas na //
T02TD1193E:35a-12: bde ba can gyi sgrar brjod do //
T02TD1193E:35a-13: zhes pa'i don lhag ma ni brda phrad sla'o //
T02TD1193E:35a-14: ljang gu mi 'jigs rigs can te ;
T02TD1193E:35a-16: ljang gu ni shin tu mdzes pa'o //
T02TD1193E:35a-17: rtog pa spangs shing dam tshig dang ldan pas na mi 'jigs rigs can zhes bya'o //
T02TD1193E:35a-21: ga pur ni byang chub kyi sems te /
T02TD1193E:35a-22: dngos su de dag gnyis dang ldan pa la bya'o //
T02TD1193E:35a-23: thabs dang shes rab rnam spangs nas //
T02TD1193E:35a-25: bo la ni thabs su 'dren la /
T02TD1193E:35a-27: kakko la ni shes rab ste //
T02TD1193E:35a-28: de gnyis spangs pas mi 'grub ces bya ba'i don to //
T02TD1193E:35a-29: mkhas pas bde chen byas nas ni //
T02TD1193E:35a-30: zhes pa la de ltar bo la dang kakko la dang ldan pas bde ba chen po byas te /
T02TD1193E:35a-31: de gnyis su med pa'i bde ba de las byung ba'i /
T02TD1193E:35a-32: mkhas pas ga pur spang mi bya //
